PharmaScan Navigation Hierarchy
├── / (Landing Page)
│   ├── /auth (Login/Register)
│   ├── /verify (Verification Page)
│   │   └── /not-verified (Verification Failed)
│   ├── /app (Consumer Dashboard)
│   └── /manufacturer (Manufacturer Portal)
│       ├── /manufacturer/dashboard (Dashboard Overview)
│       ├── /manufacturer/medicines (Medicine Management)
│       │   └── /manufacturer/create (Mint New Medicine)
│       ├── /manufacturer/generate-qr (QR Code Generation)
│       └── /manufacturer/reports (Analytics & Reports)
└── * (404 Not Found)
